    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited for whoever ends up with this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in stunning condition\u2014it seriously looks and feels like it just left the showroom! It\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and it's completely spotless inside and out. You won't find a single blemish on it. I'm looking for a good home for it where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to message me with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 43900.0,
