    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated S54 engineering. Mechanically flawless, the 3.2L inline-six features a recently overhauled Double-VANOS system and preventative rod bearing replacement using ARP hardware. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is reinforced\u2014subframe mounting points are structurally sound with zero fatigue. Suspension geometry remains factory-spec with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers. Clad in Carbon Black with an unblemished Nappa leather interior, this example exhibits zero parasitic draw or oil seepage. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
